Web3 Real Estate Fractionalization L1
Overview

Web3 Real Estate Fractionalization L1 enables shared ownership of real estate assets through tokenization.

Features
Fractional property ownership
Tokenized real estate assets
Transparent ownership records
Rental income distribution
Liquidity for real estate markets
Architecture
Asset Registry

Stores property data.

Tokenization Engine

Splits ownership into tokens.

Revenue Module

Distributes rental income.

Trading Layer

Enables asset exchange.

Use Cases
Real estate investment platforms
Property crowdfunding
Rental income sharing
Global property access
